The property is ideally located in Melbourne's Northern suburbs and is less than 32km* from the Port of Melbourne, 30km* from the CBD and 15km* from the Melbourne Airport. This property has great access to major arterials including the M80 Ring Road, Hume Freeway, Sydney Road & Cooper Street.
